1
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:31,780
♪The moon is shining above
the broken bridge, and the lake ripples♪

2
00:00:31,910 --> 00:00:37,130
♪My heart in a whirl,
with all sorts of feelings♪

3
00:00:37,230 --> 00:00:41,270
♪Clouds encircle the green hills,
and people are in distress♪

4
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:45,610
♪To help all beings, to be chivalrous♪

5
00:00:46,630 --> 00:00:50,930
♪I wish to ride the wind♪

6
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:54,960
♪It's never been done♪

7
00:00:56,050 --> 00:01:04,570
♪At this perfect moment,
you wish to exchange♪

8
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:09,750
♪A thousand of reincarnations
for a lifetime of love♪

9
00:01:10,230 --> 00:01:13,910
♪Watching the fireworks
and the full moon♪

10
00:01:14,890 --> 00:01:19,020
♪With affectionate gaze♪

11
00:01:19,780 --> 00:01:26,710
♪Accumulating lifetimes of destiny
to be with me♪

12
00:01:26,730 --> 00:01:31,550
[Different Princess]

13
00:01:34,100 --> 00:01:36,540
[Episode 35]

14
00:01:44,350 --> 00:01:46,310
Why isn't Ji Chu back yet?

15
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,760
Could it be that he's been detained

16
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,200
by the empress?

17
00:01:56,350 --> 00:01:57,230
Your Highness, there's a letter for you.

18
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:58,870
For me?

19
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:08,150
Your Highness, where are you going?

20
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:25,590
Being all mysterious,

21
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,280
so it's you.

22
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:33,160
[Anxiang Hall]

23
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:35,520
Your Highness.

24
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:38,800
Why is it so quiet?

25
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,120
Where is Princess Consort?

26
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,080
Replying to Your Highness,

27
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,080
Princess Consort left

28
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,470
half an hour ago.

29
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,960
Did she say where she was going?

30
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,240
She said she was
going to Jingzhi Library.

31
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,800
Mo Yu is following her.

32
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:54,960
It's good to have Mo Yu with her.

33
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:05,560
The gates of the palace

34
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,150
are guarded by Dingguo Army.

35
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,000
Each gate is guarded by about 50 men.

36
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:10,360
Plus all the patrols

37
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:11,000
inside the palace

38
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,000
are Dingguo Army,

39
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:13,750
about 1,000 of them in total.

40
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:17,120
Not only that,

41
00:03:17,590 --> 00:03:18,800
The streets of Shengjing

42
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,630
are also guarded by Dingguo Army.

43
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:21,750
It can be said

44
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,310
that the whole city

45
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,030
is under the empress's control.

46
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:27,840
I'm afraid

47
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:30,240
she's been planning this

48
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,240
since she arranged the marriage

49
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:34,680
between the crown prince and Lin Xiyao.

50
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:36,840
Your Highness,

51
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,800
I have some concerns.

52
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:42,360
Speak.

53
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,190
With the crown prince's attitude,

54
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,520
I'm afraid

55
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,280
it's going to be difficult for us

56
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:49,080
to rescue His Majesty.

57
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:54,310
How many men do we have?

58
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:57,000
We have 300 soldiers in the residence.

59
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,080
I'm asking about Fenglin Guards.

60
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,630
The men of sacrifice?

61
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,240
There are 52 of them now.

62
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,800
Father is now trapped in Xuanze Hall

63
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,360
which is located
in the center of the palace.

64
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:13,680
If we want to take the nearest route,

65
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,360
we can go from Anli Gate

66
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,750
to Xuanze Hall

67
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:18,480
via Tianhua Street.

68
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:20,800
Your Highness, that won't work.

69
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:22,070
The empress

70
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,750
has sent more men to guard

71
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:24,600
this route.

72
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,950
That's all the more reason
for me to take this route.

73
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,870
You mean

74
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:38,750
taking action while distracting them?

75
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,680
Yes.

76
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,750
I'll personally lead our men

77
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:46,070
down Tianhua Street.

78
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,120
Greetings, Your Highness.

79
00:04:59,830 --> 00:05:00,680
Please rise, Fang.

80
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,830
Is His Highness inside?

81
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,000
Yes, he is.

82
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:04,870
I'll go in and see him.

83
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,800
Xiyao, you're back.

84
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:36,310
I've done what you asked me

85
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:37,510
to do.

86
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,040
Thank you.

87
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:43,070
Just spare the courtesy.

88
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,510
Why are you sitting here

89
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,600
alone?

90
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,040
I just suddenly felt like

91
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,240
sitting here by myself for a while.

92
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:24,800
I'd like to sit here by myself

93
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:25,830
for a while, too.

94
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,800
Xiyao,

95
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:32,920
do you know
what a dream man of all means?

96
00:06:34,190 --> 00:06:34,920
What does it mean?

97
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:37,630
It means someone who's really nice

98
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:39,680
and everyone likes him.

99
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:49,000
I wasn't exactly

100
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,480
a good person,

101
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:53,830
but being praised by Qing

102
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:57,190
as if I were,

103
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,830
I ended up

104
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:02,920
letting Qing down.

105
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:06,240
Your Highness,

106
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,160
I don't think

107
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,560
the dream man of all

108
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:10,870
should be

109
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,510
everyone's favourite person.

110
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:18,800
Why?

111
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:22,240
Everyone in this world

112
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,040
has their own difficulties.

113
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,430
The sufferings of every individual

114
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,750
are different from each other.

115
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:34,070
We don't know others' difficulties
when we're not in their shoes.

116
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:36,070
Therefore,

117
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,510
no one will ever

118
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,870
be everyone's dream man.

119
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:45,430
But...

120
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,360
But what?

121
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:53,190
Regardless of

122
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,920
whether you are the head of East Office,

123
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:57,190
the current crown prince

124
00:07:58,310 --> 00:07:59,750
or the future emperor,

125
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:01,560
and even if you

126
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,750
want to give up the position of emperor

127
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,750
and choose to be
an ordinary zither player,

128
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:09,750
you will always be

129
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:11,070
the dream man in my heart.

130
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,360
Don't blame yourself.

131
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:22,160
If you really think

132
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,160
you've made a mistake,

133
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:25,070
it's not too late

134
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,270
to fix it.

135
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:39,670
Xiyao,

136
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:41,630
do you know

137
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,630
what my wish is?

138
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:46,870
Your wish

139
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,600
is for a stable country

140
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,840
and a peaceful world.

141
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,270
When Wan'er was little,

142
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,120
she always ran away from the palace.

143
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:04,960
She said she loved
the world outside the palace

144
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,480
and freedom,

145
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:09,360
and I always stopped her

146
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,240
so she wouldn't forget

147
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:12,750
who she was.

148
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:17,120
Now she's finally got what she wanted.

149
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:19,550
As a brother,

150
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,750
I'm really happy for her.

151
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:26,600
It turns out that you wish
to live outside the palace

152
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:28,440
as much as Ivana does.

153
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:38,080
Chu is better suited than I am

154
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:40,030
for the position behind me.

155
00:09:42,150 --> 00:09:43,870
It's a pity that Mother and Father

156
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,480
can't figure it out.

157
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,550
Wherever you go,

158
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,480
I'll always

159
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:56,750
be with you.

160
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:08,750
Thank you.

161
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:44,390
[Wanshou Hall]

162
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:46,960
Today, the new emperor is reigning,

163
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,750
and the new empress is crowned.

164
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:51,360
In response to heaven's mandate

165
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:53,120
and the people's wishes,

166
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:57,270
a massive amnesty has been granted.

167
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,660
[Wanshou Hall]

168
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:49,870
Stay alert.

169
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:50,840
What's going on?

170
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,270
Why are there so many soldiers
on the streets

171
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:54,150
instead of people?

172
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:54,670
Attention.

173
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,240
It's really strange.

174
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:00,440
These soldiers are wearing

175
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,870
the uniforms of Dingguo Army.

176
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:04,360
Did something happen in the palace?

177
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:09,440
Stop there!

178
00:12:13,540 --> 00:12:15,030
I'm calling you, you hear me?

179
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,240
Don't you know the city
is under martial law?

180
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,670
How dare you go out?

181
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:28,870
Darling,

182
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,600
I'm okay.

183
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:34,960
Sir,

184
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,270
I've just come from the countryside
with my wife

185
00:12:37,630 --> 00:12:38,240
and we don't know

186
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,480
what's going on in Shengjing

187
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,910
that it's so quiet.

188
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:42,630
Bumpkin,

189
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,030
with so many soldiers guarding out here,

190
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:45,240
this is of course a very important thing

191
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:46,200
for Liang.

192
00:12:46,990 --> 00:12:48,110
What very important thing is it?

193
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,150
Do you want to know?

194
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,550
Miss,

195
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,840
why don't you spend some time with me?

196
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,790
Sure.

197
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,600
You're so sensible.

198
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,320
Darling,

199
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:14,270
where did you get that knockout powder?

200
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,960
I took it from your medicine kit.

201
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,240
What if someone

202
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:24,240
tries to

203
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:26,080
do something to me when I'm out?

204
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,840
Of course I have to think of ways

205
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,240
to protect myself

206
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:30,840
and him.

207
00:13:32,150 --> 00:13:33,200
You're awesome.

208
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:37,240
Dingguo Army is all over the city,

209
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,150
so I think

210
00:13:40,030 --> 00:13:41,440
there's a mutiny in the palace.

211
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:44,440
It's likely that Yun is reigning.

212
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:47,600
But I don't think he'd

213
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:49,150
take the initiative.

214
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,840
So I think it's Mother

215
00:13:53,670 --> 00:13:55,200
who started it.

216
00:13:56,670 --> 00:13:58,030
If that's the case,

217
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:01,080
Chu may be in danger.

218
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:11,480
Darling,

219
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,270
I think it would be easier

220
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,080
for you to walk around

221
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,550
in this man's uniform.

222
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:19,910
Darling.

223
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:22,550
You and Chu are close friends.

224
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:23,670
I know

225
00:14:23,910 --> 00:14:25,000
you wouldn't leave him alone

226
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:27,150
if anything happened to him.

227
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,240
Go.

228
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:32,200
What about you?

229
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:35,030
Our baby and I will be waiting
for you to come home.

230
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:41,240
Let me send you

231
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,150
to Jingzhi Library.

232
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:44,000
It's all right.

233
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:45,440
Look,

234
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:47,630
I can protect myself.

235
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,360
I seem to have slept for a long time.

236
00:15:48,910 --> 00:15:50,240
Where are we?

237
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,030
We're out of the city?

238
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:07,000
Are we going to the border?

239
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:11,910
No.

240
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,390
Where's my box of jewellery?

241
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:14,670
I...

242
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,200
Where are we going?

243
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,320
Where is Ji Chu?

244
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:24,030
A divorce letter?

245
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,240
Yes.

246
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:26,480
His Highness has ordered us

247
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:28,120
to escort you to wait at the border.

248
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,440
And then?

249
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:35,240
His Highness will go to the border
to look for you

250
00:16:35,390 --> 00:16:36,840
after he's finished
with his business in Shengjing.

251
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,080
If he can't,

252
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,080
you'll be free

253
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:40,080
with this letter

254
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,150
of divorce.

255
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,200
So?

256
00:16:45,270 --> 00:16:45,960
His Highness left

257
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:46,910
this letter of divorce

258
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,320
and a box of jewellery for you.

259
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,910
This man is hilarious.

260
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:52,390
He just wants

261
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:53,600
to dump me without saying a word.

262
00:16:54,390 --> 00:16:56,000
His Highness is doing this
for your sake.

263
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:57,910
For my sake?

264
00:16:57,910 --> 00:16:58,750
Did he ask me

265
00:16:58,870 --> 00:16:59,750
for my thoughts?

266
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,550
Turn around! Back to the city!

267
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:09,480
Well...

268
00:17:09,830 --> 00:17:11,440
Not only the coachman has bad skills,

269
00:17:11,590 --> 00:17:13,310
he also has bad ears.

270
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:14,480
His Highness has ordered us

271
00:17:14,750 --> 00:17:15,400
to take you out

272
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:17,160
of Shengjing at all costs.

273
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:20,960
Fine.

274
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:24,350
Mo Yu,

275
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:26,310
if the coachman won't listen to me,

276
00:17:26,510 --> 00:17:27,510
he'll listen to you.

277
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:29,830
Tell him

278
00:17:30,030 --> 00:17:32,240
to take me back to Shengjing.

279
00:17:33,070 --> 00:17:34,880
Or I will...

280
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:36,240
I'll stab myself

281
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:37,240
in the throat with this hairpin.

282
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,000
I'll kill myself.

283
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:38,960
His Highness said

284
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:41,000
that you're not only scared of death,

285
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,240
but also very spoiled,

286
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:44,200
so you won't hurt yourself.

287
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:46,440
I don't need to be scared
by your threats.

288
00:17:48,070 --> 00:17:49,350
He looks down on me.

289
00:17:49,550 --> 00:17:50,400
I'm telling you, if I'm desperate,

290
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:51,880
I'll do anything.

291
00:18:01,510 --> 00:18:02,480
Look.

292
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:05,510
Can you take me back now?

293
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:08,000
What are you doing?

294
00:18:08,790 --> 00:18:09,400
Your Highness,

295
00:18:09,830 --> 00:18:10,880
if you try to harm yourself

296
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,270
in the slightest,

297
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:13,440
