361
00:23:00,030 --> 00:23:00,920
As you expected,

362
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,160
Prince Lv has brought his men

363
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:03,830
to Tianhua Street.

364
00:23:04,110 --> 00:23:06,070
