410
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:19,070
We are from Fengyi Palace,

411
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:20,550
serving the empress dowager.

412
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:22,200
You work for the empress dowager?

413
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:24,070
Yes.

414
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:26,030
We've got a strong backing.

415
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:27,790
Take these two women down.

416
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:30,030
Are you tired of living,

417
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:32,510
how dare you hurt
the empress dowager's men?

418
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:34,440
The empress dowager has instructed

419
00:26:34,750 --> 00:26:36,240
that anyone pretending
to be a palace maid

420
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:37,310
should be killed.

421
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:41,270
Which... Which one of your eyes can tell

422
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:42,310
