435
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:42,510
Gongye Qi.

436
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:45,200
Why... Why are you here?

437
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,110
Where is Wan'er?

438
00:27:46,920 --> 00:27:48,030
My wife is at Jingzhi Library.

439
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:51,750
I know

440
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:53,350
you usually love to join in the fun.

441
00:27:53,550 --> 00:27:54,440
But it's not really the right occasion

442
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:55,350
for you to be here today.

443
00:27:55,510 --> 00:27:56,680
Leave now. Quick.

444
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,110
