473
00:29:10,110 --> 00:29:11,880
I want to spend the rest of my time here

474
00:29:12,030 --> 00:29:13,310
with Ji Chu.

475
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:15,750
Mo Yu,

476
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,920
